channel.title: Need help Please? I'd really appreciate it
channel.description: Hey, thanks if you're reading this and can hopefully help me. I've been having problems with portforwarding. It's not the actual portforwarding i'm having problems with. It's the security part. I try to get the security to let port 43594 not be blocked, but I have no idea how. I have Norton Internet security. If anyone could help or maybe even post a video guide? I'd really appreciate it. Thanks
